      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YOU FOUND ME (8) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, giving a huge sight but headed late when a half a length second (22.96) over 400m at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Top chance in this line up. NO CHARGE (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished second (22.97) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can feature again. CHORUS LINE (3) was below best at his last start when 7th at Sale following a win (22.86) at this track two back. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Likely to be about the money. PAW INFLAME (4) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.3 lengths second (22.88) in a Grade 5 at this track.",
